，陳日君一度「黑面」拒絕回應傳媒，後來才公開交代事件，否認有關款項是政治獻金，主要用於資助慈善團體及內地地下教會，更自稱所得捐款只剩餘數十萬元。有機密資料顯示，黎智英在2012及2013年，又合共捐款600萬元予陳日君。不過，陳日君從未有拿出任何證據支持其說法，亦未有交代有關使用款項的細節<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d6da82dcc02df5b256bfaa692ef3e39abb5614","tid":1507606,"uid":135689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"我信吳律師"},{"pid":"cafc3a34d1943b82cd5781c2de170ab2162d5c06","tid":1507606,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"證據呢<br />\n冇證據當你五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f852c0c3af26e61e477834ff81f0f6fcb91a8f8e","tid":1507606,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c7c433207823ad08d17976777b3a5b60f8714ee","tid":1507606,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"125d3aa8a3db37fe866caaea49a816c398f189b0","tid":1507606,"uid":13896,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"827481157ee76ed2afb51ea786dee56506a6df6a","tid":1507606,"uid":246242,"like":41,"dislike":9,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"又五毛分化L"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"分你老母咩 有問題都唔講得？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"你咁撚樣叫問問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"又一個開post,幾隻三毛衝入嚟,玩極都無乜變化"}]}